        dc:description           "FIGURE 2. Andrusovia dybowskii Brusina in Westerlund, 1903. (a, b, e) Lectotype, locality 26 (CNHM ZMKJ 50). (c, d, f) Paralectotype, locality 26 (CNHM ZMKJ 51). (g, h) Paratype of A. brusinai, locality 22 (MSU Lc-24598). (i–k) Specimen from Baer collection, locality 26 (ZB-M W.Dyb. 70). (l, m, q) Specimen from Baer collection, locality 26 (ZB-M W.Dyb. 28). (n–p) Specimen from Baer collection, locality 26 (ZB-M W.Dyb. 28). (r, v, w) Specimen from Baer collection, locality 26 (ZB-M W.Dyb. 116). (s–u) Specimen from Baer collection, locality 26 (ZB-M W.Dyb. 70). (x) Specimen from Baer collection, locality 26 (ZB-M W.Dyb. 70). (y) Paratype of H. marina, locality 22 (MSU Lc-24614c). (z, ad) Paratype of H. marina, locality 22 (MSU Lc-24614a). (aa) Paratype of H. marina, locality 22 (MSU Lc-24614b). (ab) Specimen from Baer collection, locality 26 (ZB-M W.Dyb. 70). (ac) Specimen from Baer collection, locality 26 (ZB-M W.Dyb. 28). (ae) Paratype of A. andrusovi, locality 18 (MSU Lc-24601). Scale bar = 1 mm." ;
